#. type: Title ===
#: upstream/_guides/cassandra.adoc:261
#, no-wrap
msgid "Connecting to Apache Cassandra or DataStax Enterprise (DSE)"
msgstr "Apache CassandraまたはDataStax Enterprise(DSE)への接続"

#. type: Plain text
